  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age &gt;18 years old

          -  Chronic Rhinosinusitis without nasal polyps --- defined according to the AAO
             guidelines

          -  Elective &quot;Bilateral&quot; sinus surgery requiring at a minimum of an Uncinectomy, Maxillary
             Antrostomy, and Anterior Ethmoidectomy.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Uncorrectable coagulopathy

          -  Emergency procedure

          -  Unavailable for standard post operative follow-up

          -  Sinonasal neoplasm resections

          -  Excessive intra-operative bleeding requiring nasal packing
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
